data.description: VA assumable loan at 3%! Explore this exquisite two-story Craftsman-style residence nestled in the heart of Tacoma. At 2,153 sq. ft., this residence boasts four bedrooms, 1.75 baths, a charming front patio entrance, an open-concept living and dining area w/ wood fireplace, and a well-designed floor plan with two bedrooms and one bath on each level. The kitchen, situated towards the rear of the home, is accompanied by a compact laundry room. Other amenities include an unfinished basement w/ newer forced air unit, a fully fenced yard, and a detached one-car garage accessible from the alleyway.
